<span id="freeTextContainer1204191457987978042">Okay, I would definitely have to agree that if you have a son, if you are married to a man, if you have a brother or a father, or if you have ever had a conversation with a man you should definitely read this book!<br/>It really was just so enlightening to what makes a little boy a little boy and how those things don&apos;t really change when that boy grows up. But it&apos;s not in a Men are from Mars sort of way (or maybe it is, I actually haven&apos;t read that book!). Anyway, I am very glad that I read it. I thi</span>
