<li class='cover' id='bookCover_7497897'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/7497897-radical"><img alt="Radical: Taking Back Your Faith from the American Dream" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1333580811l/7497897._SX98_.jpg" />
